p: The title compound was obtained in 69% yield from compound 33 following the general procedure for Suzuki arylation: 1H NMR (300 MHz, CDCl 3) δ3.91 (s, 3H), 4.67 (s, 2H), 6.64 (d, J = 7.5 Hz, 1H), 7.17 (d, J = 7.8 Hz, 1H), 7.40 (t, J = 8.1 Hz, 1H), 7.51 (d, J = 8.4 Hz, 2H), 7.61 (m, 1H), 8.02 (d, J = 8.1 Hz, 2H), 8.19 (d, J = 6.6 Hz, 1H), 8.31 (s, 1H), 8.73 (s, 1H), 8.98 (s, 1H), 9.02 (s, 1H).
